(18) Flow augmentation: Need for water storage has been discussed. (20) On Salmon Distribution or Predator Interactions: Extensive fry studies have taken place on this system this year. In the late spring estimates of 40, 000 CO were made. By the end of the summer the counts were down to 4,000 due to stress from low water and exposure to predators. About 2, 000 fry were salvaged.
